Q2A
Questions to Ask the End User:

Is the issue occurring with all files or just specific files?

Are you experiencing this issue on a specific version or build of Windows 11?

Do you have any custom settings or third-party tools installed that could be affecting the behavior of Notepad?

Does the problem occur when closing files through File > Exit, or only when clicking the "X" button in the top-right corner?

Are you using a specific method to close the Notepad (e.g., keyboard shortcuts, task manager)?

Have you checked if any updates are pending for Notepad or Windows 11?

URL with Information:
You can gather information from official Microsoft documentation or trusted forums. Here’s an example:
